## 7. Persistence, SRS flavor & meta

- **localStorage** for: unlocked stages, unlocked characters, meta-currency, high scores, and an **SRS record per `sid`** (`{reps, ease, interval, due, lapses}` — mirror Hanasou’s algorithm so the data is portable).
- **SRS-as-spawn-director (“haunting”):** sentences/words the player has graded **nope/kinda** are weighted to reappear — both as preferred level-up puzzles in future runs AND, thematically, as **“haunting” word-pickups** that pulse red and lightly chase the player. The word you forgot literally hunts you until you collect + pass it. This is the spaced-repetition system reskinned as a mechanic.
- Meta-currency earned from runs (scaled by performance, incl. minigame grades) unlocks characters and permanent passives (slower spawns, longer minigame timer, auto-reveal first particle, etc.). Make some meta-upgrades *learning scaffolds* (e.g. “show romaji on chips”) so progression and pedagogy align.

