## 10. Definition of “vertical slice done” (the first milestone to hit)

A single playable run on **The Arcade** stage where: you move and auto-kill a swarm of RushFans + MerchMules, collect word-tokens, hit a level-up that opens the **Tier-A particle-only** minigame drawn from your collected words, your answer scales the upgrade with correct (bonus-framed) feedback, and you keep playing stronger. Everything else (more stages, characters, bosses, Tiers B/C, haunting, meta-shop) builds outward from that proven core.

